{"tid":218773,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"Factorio (中华人民共和国模擬器)","createTime":"2017-04-26T17:11:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-04T04:45:39.000Z","uid":11598,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3bf1159fbd398a44759135f08166da77e85e3e6d","tid":218773,"uid":11598,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T17:11:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/KVvXv1Z6EY8/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FKVvXv1Z6EY8%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=d953bbd8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KVvXv1Z6EY8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DKVvXv1Z6EY8&d=Cu9ZF5gMYzm72cT69JSRjbIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=66acd9ec\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KVvXv1Z6EY8</a><br />\n呢隻Game 叫 Factorio ，係一隻即時戰略（RTS）類型嘅遊戲<br />\n點解叫做 「中华人民共和国模擬器」？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為係呢隻驚入面，你將會扮演一個流落外星星球嘅工程師<br />\n運用你嘅知識去建造屬於你嘅自動化工廠<br />\n目的就係製造大量可以幫你生存（對抗外星怪物）、解鎖新科技（例如太陽能板！）甚至揸火車、揸坦克都得！<br />\n係建造工廠嘅同時，你亦都要小心你嘅工廠所帶來嘅環境污染<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為當你污染太多嘅時候，啲外星怪物就會一波波咁侵襲你嘅工廠<br />\n例如燒煤發電/煉油 等等都會排放污染 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可以話同支那一模一樣，比你盡情體驗先污染唔治理嘅享受 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過唔使擔心，呢隻驚有得起防火牆，可以阻隔襲擊你嘅外星怪物 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n甚至可以係上面裝機砲/雷射炮，射死啲怪物 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係好撚好玩！<br />\n<br />\n目前為止呢隻驚嘅最終目標係發射火箭<br />\n不過Factorio 其實原來已經寫咗 5 年 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然就 $150 貴啲，不過我覺得如果你係鍾意呢類型嘅話，一玩就會上癮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢隻驚其中一個特色就係可以俾你體驗自己建造屬於自己嘅貨運鐵路系統<br />\n而呢個鐵路系統嘅訊號系統更加係同現實嘅封閉式訊號系統一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n加啲訊號燈、設計路軌走向、加多個站、整架火車 你就可以係入面體驗Train Simulator <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n除咗手動駕駛之外，仲可以入定時間表等啲火車自己行 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲準時過MTR <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z1161oP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ1161oP.png&h=196e36eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我玩咗兩日嘅save <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n除咗單人mode之外，最正嘅特點就係可以多人連線，理論上仲可以去到 65536 個玩家添！<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LeHEj_sEKnw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DLeHEj_sEKnw&d=Cu9ZF5gMYzm72cT69JSRjbIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=0d7c7620\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LeHEj_sEKnw</a><br />\n有百幾個人同時玩都咪話唔壯觀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://store.steampowered.com/app/427520/Factorio/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstore.steampowered.com%2Fapp%2F427520%2FFactorio%2F&d=Cu9ZF5gMYzm72cT69JSRjbIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=cd29a368\" target=\"_blank\">http://store.steampowered.com/app/427520/Factorio/</a><br />\n而家賣緊 $150 <br />\n不過你都可以去玩官方免費 DEMO版睇下啱唔啱心水 / 海盜灣下載嘅 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有無巴打有玩？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62e77a015aaf661e58fa819dc8b635c5d3bdfde0","tid":218773,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T17:15:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9af910d665236609d92c0075414a42046f4e138","tid":218773,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T17:17:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be440e87800123773a9d50f4e677742f5bb59cb8","tid":218773,"uid":996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T17:19:23.000Z","msg":"冇玩幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1185866c805dd93f04f61d2a0668a2a236a7004d","tid":218773,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T17:20:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇玩幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85ef285fd74f14e145fb6c7770feb6c556a873ad","tid":218773,"uid":12435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T17:23:18.000Z","msg":"好耐冇玩了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之前玩過demo 後即買<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b5a4d176e38aff39122a146e123cfda01f1dd01","tid":218773,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T17:23:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好耐冇玩了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之前玩過demo 後即買<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"